        <h4 class="goldtext">Preliminary Details:</h4>
        <ul class="bullet">
            <li>Registration is open to all. Out of the registered teams only the Top 8 teams based on MLG Pro Points will be selected to compete in the League.</li>
            <li>Teams will compete in two League matches a week, scheduled across Tuesday and Thursday nights every week.</li>
            <li>The Regular Season will run for 7 weeks, from August 12th – September 25th.</li>
            <li>The Playoff bracket will be held on September 28th.</li>               
            <li>At the end of the Regular Season, the top 4 teams based on Win/Loss will advance to the Playoff bracket.</li>               
            <li>The schedule of the Regular Season will be set by ACL and all matches will be played as per the schedule. Absolutely no exceptions.</li>               
            <li>The registration fee is $100 per teams for all teams accepted into the Regular Season.</li>
            <li>The miminum prize pool is $1000.</li>
            <li>
            Registration closes on Sunday the 10th of August 11.59pm AEST and the registration fee is due on Monday the 11th of August by 8.30pm AEST.</li>
            <li>All teams accepted into the Regular Season will be contacted privately on Monday the 11th of August by Tournament Admins via the email provided in the registration email.</li>        
        </ul>

